---
title: Sesame Teriyaki Pulled Chicken Bowl with Sugar Snap Peas
description: 2021 is definitely the year of the bowl! We can't think of a better way to enjoy sesame chicken, tender rice, sweet snap peas and chewy edamame, all in one bite! You'll love this one-fork-wonder!
